title: Meet The Press - 2008-06-08 - Final Episode With Tim Russert
description:
TV Show: Meet The Press with Tim Russert (Tim&#039;s Final Episode)
Episode: NBC Political News Dream Team Joins Russert
Air Date: Sunday, June 8, 2008
Network: NBC


This is the Final episode hosted by Moderator Tim Russert before his passing just 5 days after this broadcast.

Tim is joined with NBC&#039;s "Political Dream Team" to discuss Barack Obama&#039;s capture of the 2008 Democratic nomination and Hillary Clinton&#039;s concession speech.

Guests:
- Ron Allen, NBC News Correspondent, Hillary Clinton&#039;s campaign
- Lee Cowan, NBC News Correspondent, Barack Obama&#039;s campaign
- David Gregory, Chief White House Correspondent, NBC News; Host, MSNBC&#039;s "Race for the White House"
- Andrea Mitchell, NBC News
- Kelly O&#039;Donnell, NBC News Correspondent, John McCain&#039;s campaign
- Chuck Todd, Political Director, NBC News

The World Will Miss You, Tim.

Tim Russert: May 7, 1950 - June 13, 2008
